messageBody:
Hi

According to my knowledge,
Junit comes under unit testing.
U can find the required stuff at the junit site itself.
U can find the documentation required to write the tests.
There is book called JUNIT RECIPES which may guide u in a better way.
Refer junit FAQs for more information.

Happy testing . . .

Thanks and regards
Vara Prasad.
